707926f-a.text:
1491 Second Ave., at the S.W. corner of East 78th Street, showing the lower stories of building concerned, with its stores occupied by "second hand" dealers.  Overhead is the Second Ave. Elevated Line.

714545f-a.text:
East 78th Street, north side, west from (No. 247), but not including Second Ave. Prominent building shown, is No. 205 East 78th Street, an apartment house at the N.E. corner of Third Ave.
March 29, 1937.
